  "title": "19-year-old dies in accident near filling station",
  "body_lines": [
    "COLOMBO (News 1st); A youth who was waiting in line near the Pandulagama filling station in Anuradhapura died in a road accident this morning.",
    "Police stated that the youth died on the spot after he collided with a lorry transporting heavy equipment.",
    "The deceased was identified as a 19-year-old resident of Thambuththegama.",
    "Police said that the victim was waiting in line for fuel on the left-side of the Anuradhapura \u2013 Puttlam Road.",
    "5-year no-pay leave for Public Sector to work in Private Sector?",
    "Another group of 35 people detained for illegal migration attempt to Australia"
